---
title: Mussels and Linguine with Garlic Tomato Sauce and Peppers
description: All of the elements in this dish are made for each other. Mussels, garlic and basil have nothing but love for one another and pair perfectly with a savoury tomato sauce and linguine pasta. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mussels-and-linguine-d9588ad3.jpg
